{
  "$schema": "Shopify App — Fulfillment Resource: Node data examples for all operations",
  "$notes": [
    "fieldModes convention (source: isVariableMode = fieldModes[field] !== true):",
    "  true  = constant/literal mode — value is used as-is",
    "  false = variable mode — {{nodeId.field}} references are resolved",
    "  absent = variable mode (same as false)",
    "'orderId' is a SHARED required field for all fulfillment operations",
    "Operations: create, update (tracking only), get, getMany, cancel",
    "Output for create/get/update/cancel: fulfillment.{ fulfillmentId, orderId, status, trackingNumber, trackingCompany, trackingUrl, lineItems, createdAt, updatedAt }",
    "Output for getMany: fulfillments[].{ same fields }, count"
  ],
  "examples": [
